      <title>[LO 4.4]</title>
      <para id="id5211219">MUSIC AND SYMBOLISM</para>
      <para id="id6361506"><emphasis effect="bold">Music</emphasis> plays an important role in rituals. Certain kinds of music is associated with certain rituals.</para>
      <list id="id8476998" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Listen to the music examples.</item>
        <item>Indicate which of the rituals listed below can be linked to the music.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id8332985"/>
      <list id="id1157747" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Draw any symbol that you would associate with these rituals.</item>
