      <list id="id7571281" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
        <item>The congregation joins the minister in the final hymn. There is therefore a</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id5134217">_________________________between the congregation and the minister.</para>
      <list id="id6467914" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
